OL,3,CFootball icons set aside bitter
OL,4,Crivalry to back life-saving campaign
OL,6,FITV News' Ross Arnott speaks to Ian
OL,7,FHolloway and Tom Lockyer about the
OL,8,Fcampaign.
OL,10,FTwo famous faces in the world of West
OL,11,FCountry football have set aside their
OL,12,Fclub's bitter rivalry to back a life-
OL,13,Fsaving campaign.
OL,15,FSwindon Town's Ian Holloway and
OL,16,FBristol Rovers' Tom Lockyer are urging
OL,17,Ffans across the region to learn CPR -
OL,18,Fa cause close to both of their hearts.
