OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F437A1765467142
OL,3,CFootball icons set aside bitter
OL,4,Crivalry to back life-saving campaign
OL,6,F"Me and my wife are going to do it
OL,7,F'cause I want to make a difference and
OL,8,Fwhat is 15 minutes of your time?
OL,10,F"In 15 minutes you might be able to
OL,11,Fsave some of your family's life and
OL,12,Fnot just change their life, change
OL,13,Feverybody around them. They haven't
OL,14,Flost someone when they could have
OL,15,Fdone."
OL,17,FNew figures show 8 in 10 cardiac
OL,18,Farrests happen outside of hospital,
OL,19,Fand 40,000 people who are not in
OL,20,Fhospital will have a cardiac arrest
OL,21,Fthis year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
