OL,3,CFootball icons set aside bitter
OL,4,Crivalry to back life-saving campaign
OL,6,FFor Tom Lockyer, those statistics are
OL,7,Fmore than numbers. Two years ago his
OL,8,Fheart stopped for nearly three minutes
OL,9,Fwhen he collapsed on the pitch playing
OL,10,Ffor Premier League side Luton Town.
OL,12,FHe said: "When you're laid on the
OL,13,Ffloor and you think you're dying, you
OL,14,Fcan't speak, you can't move and you
OL,15,Fsee paramedics putting a drip in your
OL,16,Farm, it's quite harrowing and tough.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
