OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F437A1765467142
OL,3,CFootball icons set aside bitter
OL,4,Crivalry to back life-saving campaign
OL,6,F"If you're listening to this and you
OL,7,Fthink, 'It'll never happen to me', I
OL,8,Fthought the same. I was at the peak of
OL,9,Fmy fitness, Premier League, and it
OL,10,Fhappened to me. It doesn't
OL,11,Fdiscriminate.
OL,13,F"When I had my cardiac arrest, I was
OL,14,Freally fortunate that it happened on a
OL,15,Fpitch and I had trained paramedics
OL,16,Fjust a mere 50 metres away.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
